<br>
&quot;ah, i have him cornered like a rat in the pantry&quot;, i muse as i wiggle my gnarled finger at him one last time before returning it to my bag of jellybellys....NO! mustn't let myself  become distracted by the sweet smooshy taste of candy and look weak in this ones eyes. i can see a bit of knowledge or power in the glitter of his eye. or maybe he is crying, i cant be sure.<br>
<br>
he takes just a second to think before giving his answer, an answer that not only satisfies my query, but takes me back for a brief moment to the days of my youth. his answer will do, yes it will do nicely, but i still cant let him off that easy...no, i must push him, must hammer him like unworked steel until i know his worth, and it just might take forever to know that.<br>
<br>
i act for a moment as though i am going to sit back down, letting segal stand and just almost regain his place at the podium, then i abrublty stand back straight and bellow, &quot;wait!&quot; segal looks as though he needs to settle his stomach, but i ignore him and stare firmly into this &quot;Q's&quot; eyes...<br>
<br>
&quot;i am afraid im not finished yet,'' i notice more sweat beading on his forehead.''there is still more i must know. &quot;<br>
<br>
i hold his gaze for what must feel like an eternity before continuing...<br>
<br>
&quot;my lad, i must know. do you know the air speed of a swallow?&quot;<br>
<br>
the air in the room thinned as i think everyone in the room gasped at once, for i think none among them anticipated &quot;the question&quot;. and all eyes turned upon the lad waiting for a response.... <p><p align=center><font color=blue><BR>---------------------------------------------<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=105791">Venerable Glovian the Wanderer</a>  </p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=265.topic"> <img src="http://www.nutrocker.co.uk/board/blPrevTopic12.gif" border=0></a><a href="http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=265.topic"> <img src="http://www.nutrocker.co.uk/board/blNextTopic12.gif" border=0> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=265.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.nutrocker.co.uk/board/blAddReply12.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.emailToFriend?topicID=265.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.threadControl?topicID=265.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=265.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=265.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan